=== P1-2: 强制 handler→service→repository 分层 ===
Card: REMEDIATION-2026-05-26 P1-2
Date: 2026-05-26
Status: ☑

--- Acceptance Criteria ---
AC1: 所有 connect handler 不再直接持有 pgxpool.Pool / clickhouse.Conn / sqlx.DB
AC2: handler→service→repository 分层：handler 只调 service 或 repository 接口
AC3: go build ./... 通过
AC4: go vet ./... 通过
AC5: go test ./internal/connect/... ./internal/repository/... ./internal/service/... 全过

--- Step 1: 违规基线 ---
修复前 7 个文件直接持有 DB 连接:
  user/auth_handler.go       — *pgxpool.Pool
  ai/ai_handler.go           — *pgxpool.Pool
  system/job_handler.go      — *pgxpool.Pool + pgx.Row/pgx.ErrNoRows
  system/schedule_health_handler.go — *pgxpool.Pool
  system/stream_handler.go   — *pgxpool.Pool (loadUserAccountIDs, computeSummary 等 4 个辅助函数)
  system/mthub_service.go    — *pgxpool.Pool (accountOwnedByUser)
  marketplace/market_handler.go — clickhouse.Conn

--- Step 2: 仓库层改造 ---

2a. AIConversationRepository: sqlx.DB → pgxpool.Pool
  方法: Create, ListByUser, GetByID, UpdateTitle, Touch, Delete, AddMessage, GetMessages
  新增: DeleteMessagesByConversation (delete messages before deleting conversation)

2b. JobRepository: sqlx.DB → pgxpool.Pool
  方法: CreateJob, GetJob, CancelJob, AddEvent, ListEvents
  移除 sqlx 特定类型，改用 pgx.Row/pgx.ErrNoRows
  scanJob 辅助函数提取为包级函数

2c. MarketDataRepository (新文件: repository/market_data_repo.go)
  构造函数: NewMarketDataRepository(ch clickhouse.Conn)
  方法: GetKlines(canonical, period, limit), GetLatestTick(canonical)
  类型: KlineBar, LatestTick

2d. ScheduleHealthRepository (新文件: repository/schedule_health_repo.go)
  构造函数: NewScheduleHealthRepository(db *pgxpool.Pool)
  方法: GetGradingConfig, GetScheduleStats, GetLatestOrderProfit, ListRunLogs, ListOrders
  类型: HealthGradingConfig, ScheduleHealthSummary, ScheduleHealthRunLog, ScheduleHealthOrder
  辅助: DefaultHealthGradingConfig()

2e. PlatformService 扩展 (service/platform_service.go)
  新增方法:
    UserOwnsAccount(ctx, userID, accountID) (bool, error)
    GetUserAccountIDs(ctx, userID) ([]string, error)
    GetUserAccountSnapshots(ctx, userID) ([]AccountSnapshot, error)
    GetUserAccountsSummary(ctx, userID) (*UserAccountsSummary, error)
  新增类型: AccountSnapshot, UserAccountsSummary

--- Step 3: Handler 更新 ---

3a. user/auth_handler.go
  Before: AuthServer{pg *pgxpool.Pool, jwtSecret, log}
  After:  AuthServer{users *repository.UserRepository, jwtSecret, log}
  changes:
    Login:      s.pg.QueryRow(...) → s.users.GetByEmail(ctx, email)
    Register:   s.pg.Exec(INSERT...) → s.users.Create(ctx, &model.User{...})
    GetMe:      s.pg.QueryRow(...) → s.users.GetByID(ctx, uid)
    RefreshToken: s.pg.QueryRow(...) → s.users.GetByID(ctx, uid)
    新增邮箱重复检查: s.users.ExistsByEmail()

3b. ai/ai_handler.go
  Before: AIServer{systemSvc, pg *pgxpool.Pool, log}
  After:  AIServer{systemSvc, conversations *repository.AIConversationRepository, log}
  changes:
    Chat:              s.pg.Exec(INSERT ai_messages) → s.conversations.AddMessage()
    ListConversations: s.pg.Query(...) → s.conversations.ListByUser()
    GetConversation:   s.pg.QueryRow+Query → s.conversations.GetByID+GetMessages
    CreateConversation: s.pg.Exec(INSERT) → s.conversations.Create()
    DeleteConversation: s.pg.Exec(DELETE) → s.conversations.DeleteMessagesByConversation + Delete
    UpdateConversationTitle: s.pg.Exec(UPDATE) → s.conversations.UpdateTitle()

3c. system/job_handler.go
  Before: JobServer{pg *pgxpool.Pool, log} + scanJobRow using pgx.Row
  After:  JobServer{jobs *repository.JobRepository, log}
  changes:
    GetJob:       scanJobRow(s.pg.QueryRow(...)) → s.jobs.GetJob(ctx, uid, jobID)
    CancelJob:    scanJobRow(s.pg.QueryRow(UPDATE...)) → s.jobs.CancelJob(ctx, uid, jobID)
    SubscribeJob: s.pg.Query(SELECT job_events) → s.jobs.ListEvents(ctx, jobID, afterSeq, 100)
    删除 scanJobRow (迁移到 repository)

3d. system/schedule_health_handler.go
  Before: ScheduleHealthServer{pg *pgxpool.Pool, log}
  After:  ScheduleHealthServer{repo *repository.ScheduleHealthRepository, log}
  changes:
    getGradingConfig: s.pg.QueryRow(SELECT system_configs) → s.repo.GetGradingConfig()
    GetScheduleHealth: 5 个独立查询 → s.repo.GetScheduleStats + GetLatestOrderProfit + ListRunLogs + ListOrders
    删除 healthGradingConfig struct + defaultHealthGradingConfig (迁移到 repository)

3e. system/stream_handler.go
  Before: StreamServer{svc, pg *pgxpool.Pool, log}
  After:  StreamServer{svc, platform *service.PlatformService, log}
  changes:
    loadUserAccountIDs:   s.pg.Query(SELECT mt_accounts) → s.platform.GetUserAccountIDs()
    sendInitialSnapshot:  s.pg.Query(SELECT mt_accounts) → s.platform.GetUserAccountSnapshots()
    computeSummary:       s.pg.Query(SELECT aggregate mt_accounts) → s.platform.GetUserAccountsSummary()
    userOwnsAccount:      s.pg.QueryRow(SELECT EXISTS) → s.platform.UserOwnsAccount()
    删除 4 个独立 DB 辅助函数 (loadUserAccountIDs, computeSummary, userOwnsAccount 已移至 PlatformService)

3f. system/mthub_service.go
  Before: MtHubServer{svc, pg *pgxpool.Pool, log}
  After:  MtHubServer{svc, platform *service.PlatformService, log}
  changes:
    accountOwnedByUser (5 处调用) → s.platform.UserOwnsAccount()
    删除独立 accountOwnedByUser 函数

3g. marketplace/market_handler.go
  Before: MarketServer{platform, ch clickhouse.Conn, nc, log}
  After:  MarketServer{platform, marketData *repository.MarketDataRepository, nc, log}
  changes:
    GetKlines:      s.ch.Query(SELECT FROM kline) → s.marketData.GetKlines()
    GetSymbolStats: s.ch.QueryRow(SELECT FROM tick_raw) → s.marketData.GetLatestTick()

--- Step 4: main.go 构造更新 ---

新增 repository 实例化 (插入在 handler 构造之前):
  userRepo       := repository.NewUserRepository(pool)
  convRepo       := repository.NewAIConversationRepository(pool)
  jobRepo        := repository.NewJobRepository(pool)
  schedHealthRepo := repository.NewScheduleHealthRepository(pool)
  marketDataRepo  := repository.NewMarketDataRepository(ch)

构造调用变更:
  user.NewAuthServer(pool, ...)           → user.NewAuthServer(userRepo, ...)
  system.NewMtHubServer(mthubSvc, pool)   → system.NewMtHubServer(mthubSvc, platformSvc)
  mktplace.NewMarketServer(platformSvc, ch, nc) → mktplace.NewMarketServer(platformSvc, marketDataRepo, nc)
  ai.NewAIServer(aiSvc, pool)             → ai.NewAIServer(aiSvc, convRepo)
  system.NewStreamServer(mthubSvc, pool)  → system.NewStreamServer(mthubSvc, platformSvc)
  system.NewJobServer(pool)               → system.NewJobServer(jobRepo)
  system.NewScheduleHealthServer(pool)    → system.NewScheduleHealthServer(schedHealthRepo)

